        {
            "title": "三檔遭重挫的軟體股今日強勁反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cnuI5Tv_0wsbw9g616LjUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_3_M_1440047966.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Atlassian、Twilio和Five9週五盤前交易中大幅上漲,三家公司均在週四收盤後公布了優於預期的財報,為承壓已久的軟體板塊注入了一劑強心針。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Atlassian領漲,盤前上漲21.9%,該公司公布第三財季每股收益為1.75美元,較預期高出0.77美元,營收為17.9億美元,超過15.7億美元的市場共識預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays表示,這份財報應能吸引新的投資者關注該股。\"整個軟體板塊的預期本就偏低,尤其是TEAM,考慮到近期股價的疲軟表現。這些業績很可能會吸引更多投資者重新審視這檔股票,\"該行表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fb2535fd-61d7-3835-a018-620bf1fdd281-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BMO Capital分析師Keith Bachman在財報公布後維持跑贏大盤評級,但將目標價從130美元下調至105美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>Twilio</span></span></span></span>盤前上漲18.4%,該公司公布第一季每股收益為1.50美元,較預期高出0.23美元,營收為14.1億美元,超過13.4億美元的市場共識預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司將全年報告營收增長預期從此前的11.5%–12.5%上調至14%–15%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行分析師Koji Ikeda將該股目標價從190美元上調至225美元,維持買入評級,理由是毛利潤金額增長從第四季的10%加速至同比增長16%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>Five9</span></span></span></span>盤前上漲16.4%,該公司公布第一季每股收益為0.76美元,較預期高出0.08美元,營收為3.053億美元,超過2.999億美元的市場共識預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Needham分析師Scott Berg重申買入評級,強調AI營收同比增長82%,以及該公司長期美元留存率趨勢出現反轉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%89%E6%AA%94%E9%81%AD%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E7%9A%84%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-124554069.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 21:12:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美伊停火了卻還是過不去？阿聯一句話揭荷姆茲危機根本沒解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nQsKvYE0YkWJ04RDHPMB1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/d89ec956a5cc38da20689cb67a59a963\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
